Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.62,0:23:21.99,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)\c&HC3D0FA&\3c&H707DA1&}纵使待到早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.99,0:23:24.09,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}纵使待到早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.09,0:23:26.26,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}云雾也不会散去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.26,0:23:28.66,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}纵使太阳升起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.66,0:23:31.29,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}也无法看见你
