Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.26,0:23:38.00,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)\fad(0,500)}也一笑了之 继续追寻那份光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:40.50,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}享受现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:42.74,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}充满谜团的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.74,0:23:45.14,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}无法解开的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.14,0:23:47.54,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}满是罪孽的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.54,0:23:50.01,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}每天的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.01,0:23:50.71,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}请给予我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.71,0:23:53.02,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}那已知的今天与未知的明天的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.02,0:23:55.25,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}就此启程去寻找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.25,0:23:57.45,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}那声音
